data.description: Country Living yet close to town is the nicely updated ranch style home. Just over 3/4 acre is this 3 bd 2 ba home w/office space & was freshly painted and new flooring throughout. The kitchen has a pantry, new oven/range,dishwasher & SS sink. Lots of ceiling fans, vaulted ceiling in master which is 14 x 27. A blazing pellet stove keeps you nice and toasty! Both bathrooms have been painted & new vinyl flooring. There's a separate shop plumbed for water 19x20. Storage shed 8x10. Garage 24x24 and above is 576sf guest quarters 1 bd 1 ba w/sep hot water heater. There are in ground sprinklers throughout the property & the landscaped yard has several fruit trees walnut, cherry, pear, plum, apples & grapes. RV parking w/full hook-ups. Front & back covered porches plus a patio area. Lg fenced garden & fully fenced bk yard w/double gate entry to rear yard and driveway. Custom chicken coop is fenced off and there's also motion lights around the house. This could be your very own mini ranch.
